include ../mixins/icon

block services
    article#servicesContent.services-content
        #servicesContentTop.services-content-top
            .center
                +icon('Digital Branding', 'images/services-icon-digital-branding.png')
                +icon('Social Solutions', 'images/services-icon-social-solutions.png')
                +icon('Brand Promotion', 'images/services-icon-brand-promotion.png')
        .center
            section.context
                h2 OUR SERVICES
                img.ctx-image(src="images/services-phone-ad.png" alt="Our Services")
                .txt-block
                    p Leverage the world's most advanced native ads platform to delight users with ads that blend seamlessly into your app's content.
                    p Build, run, and measure mobile rich-media ads with our simple, yet powerful, cloud-based platform. It is the only HTML5 visual authoring platform created specifically for the mobile marketplace. Built by designers, for designers.
                    p Take the guess work out of whether or not your ads reach your audience, and start paying less to attain more.
                    p When you partner with us, your ads...
                    ul.orange
                        li Last longer
                        li Cost less (less than a penny per view)
                        li Can't be blocked, skipped or ignored
                        li Reach a targeted, captivated audience
                        li Reach mobile viewers